FRANK BENNETT v. LAURA LUCILE RYALS BENNETT, insane and single, et al. 26 So. (2nd) 505

January Terna, 1946

May 28, 1946 Division A *513Cooper & Cooper, for plaintiff. Forrest 0. Hobbs, for defendant. PER CURIAM:

The certified question propounded in the above cause is not answered because the question is not within the purview of Section 59.32 Florida Statutes 1941, Cumulative Supplement 1945. See Schwob Company of Florida v. Florida Industrial Commission 152 Fla. 202, 11 So. (2nd) 782.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BUFORD and ADAMS, JJ„ concur.
